Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:13:01.84,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\fad(525,525)\fnArial\b1\fs56.5\4a&HFF&\pos(960,1065)\bord2.4}Amiral de la grande flotte Yonta Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.81,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\fad(525,0)\fnArial\b1\fs66.5\4a&HFF&\pos(960,810)\bord2.4}Cavendish  –  Pirate
